      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
    
          <div class="govspeak">
<p>The chair of the Migration Advisory Committee, Professor Brian Bell, writes to the Rt Hon Oliver Dowden MP, Secretary of State for the Department for Digital, Culture, Media & Sport (DCMS), responding to the DCMS’s <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/uk-national-data-strategy/national-data-strategy" class="govuk-link">National Data Strategy</a>.</p>
</div>

</div>
